article_title: Wasserman Schultz: 5 issues to kill Trump, 'nightmare is now a reality'
article_text:
The Democratic National Committee is quickly turning its focus and guns on presumptive Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump, with the party boss laying out a five-point plan to "STOP DONALD TRUMP."

"Donald Trump will be the Republican Party's nominee for president. This nightmare is now a reality."

article_metadata.description:
The Democratic National Committee is quickly turning its focus and guns on presumptive Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump, with the party boss laying out a five-point plan to STOP DONALD TRUMP.
A fundraising package signed by Chairwoman Rep. Debbie Wasserman Schultz, declares:
Donald Trump will be the Republican Party's nominee for president. This nightmare is now a reality.



In calling on Democrats to set up a wall to block the New York businessman's path to the White House, it presented five key issues for the fall election built on some of the headline-grabbing comments made by Trump.
